At the beginning of the measurement average fuel consumption is 4,7 l/100km.

00:00:32.000 --> 00:00:37.200
At the end of measurement average fuel consumption at 90 km/h is 3,1 l/100km.

00:00:39.200 --> 00:00:49.440
This time cruise control is set to 123 km/h which gives 120 km/h on DriftBox.

00:00:51.360 --> 00:01:01.360
